================================================================================

aozora-epub depends on the `aozora` library crates consumed via git tag
dep, to convert aozora `.txt` sources into the XHTML fragments that
EPUB3 spine items embed. aozora is dual-licensed Apache-2.0 OR MIT;
see https://github.com/P4suta/aozora/blob/main/NOTICE for the
third-party attributions.


