2. Prior art: AozoraEpub3 family (acknowledgement)
================================================================================

There is an established ecosystem of aozora→EPUB3 converters which this
project does **not** replace:

- [hmdev/AozoraEpub3](https://github.com/hmdev/AozoraEpub3) — the
  original Java converter, the de-facto standard.
- [whiteleaf7/AozoraEpub3](https://github.com/whiteleaf7/AozoraEpub3)
  — fork.
- [Improved AozoraEpub3 (kyukyunyorituryo / 急急如律令)](https://kyukyunyorituryo.github.io/aozoraepub/)
  — fork targeting 電書協 EPUB3 制作ガイド compliance + Android port.

aozora-epub is parked until a clear differentiating need emerges
(see ADR-0001). Until then, AozoraEpub3 family tools are the
recommended choice for users converting aozora `.txt` to EPUB3.


